fullplot: Story revolves around a young boxer, Izzy Daniels, who trains to follow in his father's footsteps by winning the Golden Glove. When his friend, Mary, however, asks him to substitute for a team member in a Double Dutch tournament, the young man discovers a hidden passion for jump roping
plot: A teenager is pressured by his father to become a boxer - but a local girl introduces him to the very different sport of rope-jumping.
title: Jump In!
